episodes.title: The Killing Hour Cult The Insanity of The Alexander Family
episodes.description:
Dive into the dark and chilling tale of the Alexander family, twisted by zealous religious beliefs from The Lorber Society. Uncover the shocking events that unfolded, leaving a trail of destruction.
